        Parameters:
        Sender - the ID of the sensor
        Timestamp - the timestamp when this Event has been created
        PositionX - the position of this sensor on the x-axis
        PositionY - the position of this sensor on the y-axis
        PositionZ - the position of this sensor on the z-axis
        Velocity - the velocity of this sensor
        Acceleration - the accelartion of this sensor
        VelocityX - the velocity of this sensor on the x-axis
        VelocityY - the velocity of this sensor on the y-axis
        VelocityZ - the velocity of this sensor on the z-axis
        AccelerationX - the accelartion of this sensor on the x-axis
